{
        let cellWidth = ((Int(UIScreen.main.bounds.width) - 32) / NumberConstants.collectionViewCellWidthCount) - 8
        
        let layout = UICollectionViewFlowLayout()
        layout.sectionInset = UIEdgeInsets(top: 0, left: 0, bottom: 100, right: 0)
        layout.headerReferenceSize = CGSize(width: 0, height: 164)
        layout.itemSize = CGSize(width: cellWidth, height: cellWidth + 60)
        
        let collectionView = UICollectionView(frame: .zero, collectionViewLayout: layout)
        collectionView.backgroundColor = .black
        collectionView.showsVerticalScrollIndicator = false
        collectionView.showsHorizontalScrollIndicator = false
        collectionView.register(ChooseCollectionViewCell.self, forCellWithReuseIdentifier: ChooseCollectionViewCell.reuseIdentifier)
        
        collectionView.translatesAutoresizingMaskIntoConstraints = false
        
        return collectionView
    }()
